@startuml
title Ingest UML 总览图（L0 导航）

' Scope:
' - 展示 ingest 图谱分层与阅读入口
' Not in scope:
' - 不描述具体时序与字段
' See also:
' - ./acceptance/ingest-acceptance-boundary.puml
' - ./execution/ingest-execution-boundary.puml
' - ./shared/ingest-shared-state-machine.puml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

package "L0 总览" as L0 {
  rectangle "入口 API\nupload/status/preview/reprocess/delete" as API
}

package "L1 责任域" as L1 {
  rectangle "Acceptance\n上传受理 + 状态查询" as ACC
  rectangle "Execution\nworker/retry/preview/reprocess/delete" as EXE
}

package "L2 共享权威图" as L2 {
  rectangle "State Machine\n唯一状态定义" as STM
  rectangle "ER / Domain\n唯一结构定义" as ERD
}

API --> ACC : 受理与可追踪
API --> EXE : 执行与运维动作
ACC --> STM : 引用
EXE --> STM : 引用
ACC --> ERD : 引用
EXE --> ERD : 引用

note bottom
推荐阅读顺序：
1) 本图（L0）
2) L1 责任域边界图
3) L1 单用例时序图
4) L2 共享权威图
end note

@enduml
